features: Size: Each sticker measures 100mm x 150mm (6" x 4"), perfect for clear visibility on wheelie bins and other outdoor containers
Customisation: Personalised with your house number and street name in bold, clear text for easy identification
Durability: Waterproof and weatherproof construction ensures long-lasting performance in all weather conditions, maintaining clarity and adhesion
Pack Contents: Set of 4 identical self-adhesive stickers allowing for multiple bin labelling or replacement as needed
Easy Application: Peel-and-stick design allows for quick, straightforward application on clean, dry surfaces
description: Transform your wheelie bin into an easily identifiable container with our premium personalised bin number stickers. Each pack includes 4 high-quality, waterproof stickers measuring 100mm x 150mm, perfect for displaying your house number and street name. These durable adhesive labels are specifically designed to withstand various weather conditions, from rain to sunshine, ensuring your bin information remains clear and legible throughout the seasons. The bold, clear typography makes it simple to spot your bin from a distance, particularly useful on collection days or in shared spaces. Installation is straightforward - simply peel and stick to any clean, dry surface on your bin. These stickers are ideal for residential homes, helping to prevent bin mix-ups with neighbours and making it easier for waste collection teams to identify the correct location. The classic black and white design maintains a professional appearance while serving a practical purpose. Compatible with standard wheelie bins, these stickers help maintain organisation in your outdoor space with minimal effort.
